channel.title: You Me At Six
channel.description:
I think they will become real big. There music gets better and better.
Their Myspace: http://www.myspace.com/youmeatsix
[b]Just a few of their songs[/b] Gossip: http://youtube.com/watch?v=lqyIMODMmbI Save it for the bedroom: http://youtube.com/watch?v=4cidd5eBViA You've made you bed (No vid): http://youtube.com/watch?v=Py3rKXLnvOs If i were in your shoes: http://youtube.com/watch?v=na7dwYv0Y-I The Rumour (No vid): http://youtube.com/watch?v=8HBmzrz1kuk
[i]There are more songs but these are the ones i recommend you listen to to get into their vibe :P[/i]
[b]Some vids of them supporting angels and airwaves (vids are shit)[/b] http://youtube.com/watch?v=LhXQ_FA5iPY http://youtube.com/watch?v=pkQzNmuAK4Q
[b]Review[/b]
http://www.noizemakesenemies.co.uk/2008/04/angels-and-airwaves-you-me-at-six.html
Yes, from the concert i saw but they have a paragraph which sums up You Me At Six
